# ── Markdown & AI assistant rules (local-only) ───────────────
# Only README files reach the remote. Every other .md (internal docs,
# the audit log, OSS templates) and the .cursorrules workflow file stay
# local and never appear on GitHub.
*.md
!README.md
!**/README.md
.cursorrules
